data.description: WELCOME HOME to this beautiful 4 bedroom corner lot home sitting on .34 acres. This home gives you great curb appeal with a side entry garage, and stone accents around the bay window and front porch. This open concept home greets you with tons of natural light, separate dining room off the kitchen, new LVP flooring, and freshly painted walls. Upstairs you will find a spacious primary bedroom, ensuite with double vanity, garden tub, separate shower and spacious walk in closet. Relaxing evenings await you with a covered deck and fenced in backyard. This home will have you ready to make an offer in no time!
